description: Stockwik Förvaltning AB is engaged in providing investment services. The company is headquartered in Taby, Stockholm and currently employs 261 full-time employees. The company went IPO on 2019-02-21. The Company’s portfolio comprises BergFast AB, which is engaged in external property management and gardening; Aktiv Fastighets Forvaltning i Nacka AB (AFF), which deals with technical property management, land management, source sorting and refurbishments; Kallhalls Rot & VVS-system AB (KRVVS), active within area of plumbing; as well as Vaxholms Varmeservice AB, an electrical and plumbing installation company.
naicsSector: Administrative and Support and Waste Management and Remediation Services
